---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Net Promoter Score View
description: a read-only display of a Net Promoter Score
---

{% from "components/net-promoter-score-view/macro.njk" import netPromoterScoreView %}

<h2>Detractors (0–6)</h2>
<p>0: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 0 }) }}</p>
<p>3: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 3 }) }}</p>
<p>6: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 6 }) }}</p>

<h2>Passives (7–8)</h2>
<p>7: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 7 }) }}</p>
<p>8: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 8 }) }}</p>

<h2>Promoters (9–10)</h2>
<p>9: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 9 }) }}</p>
<p>10: {{ netPromoterScoreView({ value: 10 }) }}</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The view has an <code>aria-label</code> that includes the value
  and category (Detractor, Passive, or Promoter) so screen readers
  announce the meaning regardless of the visual styling.</p>
